on may be triggered in downstream applications. This issue is fixed in version 9.0.0. For complete details refer to the referenced GHSL-2021-023.','2021-06-12',6.8,8.8,8,'https://github.com/Abady0x1/CVE-2021-32819'),('CVE-2021-36394','In Moodle, a remote code execution risk was identified in the Shibboleth authentication plugin.','2022-04-26',0,9.8,0,'https://github.com/lavclash75/CVE-2021-36394-Pre-Auth-RCE-in-Moodle'),('CVE-2021-43789','PrestaShop is an Open Source e-commerce web application. Versions of PrestaShop prior to 1.7.8.2 are vulnerable to blind SQL injection using search filters with `orderBy` and `sortOrder` parameters. The problem is fixed in version 1.7.8.2.','2022-01-28',7.5,9.8,7.5,'https://github.com/numanturle/CVE-2021-43789'),('CVE-2021-30461','A remote code execution issue was discovered in the web UI of VoIPmonitor before 24.61. When the recheck option is used, the user-supplied SPOOLDIR value (which might contain PHP code) is injected into config/configuration.php.','2021-05-06',7.5,9.8,0,'https://github.com/daedalus/CVE-2021-30461'),('CVE-2021-44735','Embedded web server command injection vulnerability in Lexmark devices through 2021-12-07.','2023-07-20',10,9.8,0,'https://github.com/defensor/CVE-2021-44735'),('CVE-2021-3345','_gcry_md_block_write in cipher/hash-common.c in Libgcrypt version 1.9.0 has a heap-based buffer overflow when the digest final function sets a large count value. It is recommended to upgrade to 1.9.1 or later.','2021-01-31',7.2,7.8,0,'https://github.com/MLGRadish/CVE-2021-3345'),('CVE-2021-44529','A code injection vulnerability in the Ivanti EPM Cloud Services Appliance (CSA) allows an unauthenticated user to execute arbitrary code with limited permissions (nobody).','2022-03-24',7.5,9.8,0,'https://github.com/jkana/CVE-2021-44529'),('CVE-2021-27928','A remote code execution issue was discovered in MariaDB 10.2 before 10.2.37, 10.3 before 10.3.28, 10.4 before 10.4.18, and 10.5 before 10.5.9; Percona Server through 2021-0